  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        met at least one of the following criteria: oliguria (urine output less than 100 mL in a 6
        h period and unresponsive to fluid resuscitation), serum potassium concentration more than
        6.5 mmol/L, severe acidemia (pH &lt; 7.2), serum creatinine more than 250 µmol/L, or presence
        of severe organ edema (e.g. pulmonary edema).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  were presence of a malignant tumor, chronic renal insufficiency (serum creatinine &gt;133
             µmol/L), or receiving any kind of renal replacement therapy before randomization.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
